      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WYNDRA ALL HEART (8) broke from a low draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only 2 lengths (29.88) behind Elsa Above at this track. Has a win and two minor placings from three starts from this draw. Key chance in this line up. ZIPPER IN (7) made light work of a wide draw last time with a slick early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing third (29.75) at this track over 520m. Has good speed and will be prominent from out wide. Can measure up. ELLE'S MOON (2) broke from the inside draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only one length (29.75) behind Peloponnese at Nowra. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Expected to be in the finish again. NIGHT AGENT (4) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
